       PROCEDURE       DIVISION.

       ROT-000-000.
           DISPLAY  TLA-001  TLA-002
           OPEN     I-O      CADLDP
                    INPUT    CADDSP
           ACCEPT   DTA-SYS    FROM    DATE
           MOVE     12       TO  ANO-SYS
           IF  MES-SYS   <   12  MOVE 13  TO  ANO-SYS.

       ROT-100-000.
           DISPLAY  LPA-SUF
                    LPA-ATV  MEN-001
           MOVE     0   TO   PRX-DSP
           ACCEPT   (08 33)  PRX-DSP  WITH  UPDATE  AUTO-SKIP
           ACCEPT            TECLADO  FROM  ESCAPE  KEY
           IF  TECLADO   =   01
               GO  TO        ROT-200-000.
           IF  PRX-DSP   <   1  OR  >  6
               GO  TO        ROT-100-000.
           MOVE     ATV-TAB (PRX-DSP) TO  ATV-AUX
           DISPLAY  PRX-ENT  ATV-ENT.

       ROT-100-010.
           DISPLAY  LPA-DES
                    LPA-DIA  MEN-002
           MOVE     0    TO  SUF-DSP
           ACCEPT   (08 35)  SUF-DSP  WITH  UPDATE  AUTO-SKIP
           ACCEPT            TECLADO  FROM  ESCAPE  KEY
           IF  TECLADO   =   01
               GO  TO        ROT-100-000.
           IF  SUF-DSP   =   ZEROS
               GO  TO        ROT-100-010.
           MOVE     SPACES   TO  RSP-OPC
           READ     CADDSP   INVALID KEY
                    DISPLAY  MEN-003
                    ACCEPT   OPC-001
                    GO  TO   ROT-100-010.
           DISPLAY  SUF-ENT      DES-ENT
           MOVE     SPACES   TO  HST-LDP
           MOVE     ZEROS    TO  DTA-AUX  VAL-AUX.

       ROT-100-020.
           DISPLAY  LPA-MES  MEN-004
           ACCEPT   (12 33)  DIA-AUX  WITH  UPDATE  AUTO-SKIP
           ACCEPT            TECLADO  FROM  ESCAPE  KEY
           IF  TECLADO   =   01
               GO  TO        ROT-100-010.
           IF  DIA-AUX   <   1  OR  > 31
               GO  TO        ROT-100-020.
           DISPLAY  DIA-ENT.

       ROT-100-030.
           DISPLAY  LPA-ANO
           ACCEPT   (12 36)  MES-AUX  WITH  UPDATE  AUTO-SKIP
           ACCEPT            TECLADO  FROM  ESCAPE  KEY
           IF  TECLADO   =   01
               GO  TO        ROT-100-020.
           IF  MES-AUX   <   1  OR  > 12
               GO  TO        ROT-100-030.
           DISPLAY  MES-ENT.

       ROT-100-040.
           DISPLAY  LPA-HST  MEN-004
           ACCEPT   (12 39)  ANO-AUX  WITH  UPDATE  AUTO-SKIP
           ACCEPT            TECLADO  FROM  ESCAPE  KEY
           IF  TECLADO   =   01
               GO  TO        ROT-100-030.
           DISPLAY  ANO-ENT.

       ROT-100-050.
           DISPLAY  LPA-VAL  MEN-005
           ACCEPT   (13 33)  HST-LDP  WITH  UPDATE
           ACCEPT            TECLADO  FROM  ESCAPE  KEY
           IF  TECLADO   =   01
               GO  TO        ROT-100-040.
           DISPLAY  HST-ENT.

       ROT-100-060.
           DISPLAY  LPA-VAL  MEN-006
           ACCEPT   (15 32)  VAL-AUX  WITH  UPDATE
           ACCEPT            TECLADO  FROM  ESCAPE  KEY
           IF  TECLADO   =   01
               GO  TO        ROT-100-050.
           IF  VAL-AUX   =   ZEROS
               GO  TO        ROT-100-060.
           DISPLAY  VAL-ENT  MEN-007
           MOVE     " "  TO  RSP-OPC
           ACCEPT   OPC-001
           ACCEPT   TECLADO  FROM ESCAPE  KEY
           IF  TECLADO   =   01
               GO  TO        ROT-100-060.
           MOVE     CHV-DSP  TO  COD-LDP
           MOVE     DTA-SYS  TO  DTA-LDP
           MOVE     DTA-AUX  TO  PGT-LDP
           MOVE     VAL-AUX  TO  VAL-LDP
